[{"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Oberfinanzdirektion M\u00fcnster S-2227 - 76 - St 11 - 31S-2227 -EStG: 21BdF letter IV B 1 - S-2253 - 139/84 v"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "15 11 1984 BStBl I 561 Income tax treatment of usufruct and other rights of use in the case of income from renting and leasing Reference: Circular decree of 17 12 1984 S-2227 - 76 - St 11 - 31 ESt-Nr 104/1984 to \u00a7 21 EStGRundverordnung of 12 3 1985 S- 2227 - 76 - St 11 - 31 ESt-Nr 16/1985 to \u00a7 21 EStG 1 Free usufruct 2 usufruct ordered against payment 3 usufruct partly against payment 4 usufruct with reservation / right of residence 5 mandatory \"donation\" right of usufruct 6 not in real possession 7 Reserved usufruct in the case of transfer of real estate against payment I am hereby sending a number of example cases for the treatment of usufruct and other rights of use under income tax law according to the usufruct decree of 15 11 1984 BStBl 1984 IS"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "561 ff"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The example cases are intended as a working aid for the assessment areas"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "1 Free usufruct 11 Karl Reich (R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") gave his underage daughter Nadine (N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") ordered the gross usufruct of two rented residential properties for ten years on December 31, 1979"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The district court had refused the appointment of a nurse to conclude the contract"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The usufruct is entered in the land register"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The rental income of 100,000 DM annually was transferred by the tenants to an account of the N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "deposited"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "borne alone (annually including the larger maintenance costs and the depreciation fee 50,000 DM)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The income tax assessments 1982 and 1983 of the R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and the N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "are under VdN"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution The usufruct is to be recognized for tax purposes despite the lack of a caretaker appointment (No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessments 1982 and 1983 R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV0 DM (Item 23) 100,000 DM (Item 10 ff) Advertising expenses 50,000 DM +0 DM (Items 19 - 21) Income- 50,000 DM 100,000 DM + Item 64 i"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "the decree of the FinM NRW of 25 5 1981 S-2190 - 12 - V B 1 (= Rdvfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "from 29 6 1981 S-2227 - 101 - St 11 - 31 ESt-Nr 59/1981) and decrees of the FinM NRW from 15 1 and 27 8 1982 S-2190 - 12 - VB 1 (= Rdvfgen from 17 2 and 11 10 1982 S-2227 - 101 - St 11 - 31 VAT no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "16/1982 and 104/1982) income tax assessments 1984 ffR"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV0 DM (Item 23) 100,000 DM (Item 10 ff) Commercial expenses0 DM (Item 24) 0 DM (Item 19-21) Income from VuV0 DM100000 DM12 Variant of circumstances (contract change with regard to bearing the burden) By notarial contract of 2 January 1985 R."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "that N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "from 1 1 1984 has to bear all costs for the land"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "At the same time, R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "his daughter's further fortune"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "A supplementary nurse was involved in changing the contract; the guardianship court has approved the change"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In accordance with the contract, N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "her father in 1985 the costs incurred for 1984 (excluding depreciation) in the amount of 40,000 DM"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The amendment to the usufruct agreement is effective under civil law"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The child was represented by a supplementary carer (Section 1909 Paragraph 1 BGB); the guardianship court approval of the contract amendment (\u00a7 1821 Paragraph 1 No. 1 BGB) is available"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The change must be taken into account for tax purposes from VZ 1984 (Item 61)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The usufructuary pays or"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "does not reimburse the land costs until 1985; However, due to the tax recognition of the retroactive effect, it is possible to deduct the expenses already in the 1984 income tax assessment of the N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "to be considered as income-related expenses (Item 21)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessment 1984 R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "as with 110 DMESt assessment 1984 N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV100000 DM Advertising costs 40000 DM (Item 21) Income from VuV60000 DM13 Factual variant (replacement) R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "agree on November 2, 1985 with the involvement of an additional guardian and with the consent of the Guardianship Court, the replacement of the usufruct on November 1, 1984 against payment of a reasonable amount of DM 400,000 by R."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The father transfers 300,000 DM to the daughter on October 1, 1985 (400,000 DM minus the rental income of 100,000 DM received by N in 1984)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The replacement of the usufruct also falls under Item 61"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "From a tax point of view - even for the past - no disadvantageous conclusions are to be drawn from the redemption, even if the usufruct up to the time of redemption or"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has not existed for 5 years up to the date on which the replacement was agreed (1 1 1984)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "(If the usufruct is canceled with retroactive effect from the time of the conclusion of the contract, it must be checked whether \u00a7 12 No. 2 EStG is applicable"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") The ones from N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Rents received in 1984 are to be recorded in the income tax assessment 1984 of the R due to the regulation in Item 61"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The transfer payment can be made by R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "neither deducted in income tax assessment 1984 (pro rata) nor in 1985 as income-related expenses; at N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "the transfer payment is not part of the taxable income (Item 25)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessment 1984 R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV100000 DM0 DMAdvertising costs50000 DM0 DMIncome from VuV50000 DM0 DM14 Situation variant (replacement) Situation as in 13; N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "can keep the rent received in 1984 and continues to receive from R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "the gross rents"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution The income tax assessments of R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "are to be carried out as under 13"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The renunciation of the repayment of the rental income by the former usufructuary is at R as a non-deductible benefit i"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "\u00a7 12 No. 2 EStG (cf. also No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Should for N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "A final assessment in 1984 already existed, this can be corrected in accordance with Section 175 (1) sentence 1 no.2 AO"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "15 Situation variant (missing land register entry) Situation as in 11; the usufruct was actually carried out, but not entered in the land register"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In the case of the income tax assessments of the R under VdN for 1982 and 1983, the usufruct has not been recognized for tax purposes"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The tax office has accordingly not carried out any assessments for N."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution It is a validly agreed mandatory right of use i"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Section 4 of the usufruct decree"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The income from the rental is for all open assessments N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "attributable (No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "54 b)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "R can no longer deduct the expenses it bears for the property as income-related expenses (no"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "54 d)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The transitional regulations on the deduction of advertising expenses by the owner mentioned in the solution to 11 only concern real rights of use; they are therefore not applicable here"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "For N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "income tax assessments are still to be carried out; In this case, income from VuV in the amount of DM 100,000 must be taken as a basis (Item 54 b)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Due to the lack of actual costs, the deduction for advertising expenses does not apply"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessments 1982 ff R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV0 DM100000 DMAdvertising costs0 DM0 DMIncome from VuV0 DM100000 DMTake note of transitional regulation On a matching request from R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and N"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "No. 53 and 54 of the usufructuary decree of 23 11 1983 BStBl I S"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "508 for 1982 and 1983 continue to be used (No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In this case, R"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "continue to attribute the income; he can continue to deduct the advertising expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "2 Benefit usufruct ordered against payment Hermann Sorge (p"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "), who for reasons of age no longer wants to take care of the management of his rental property with 10 apartments of the same size, has referred the lawyer Gustav Dreher (D"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") appointed usufruct in rem on the property for 15 years"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "According to the contract, all expenses for the property are to be borne, in addition to \u00a7 1041 BGB, including the non-ordinary maintenance expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "paid an amount of DM 300,000 for the usufruct on December 1, 1984"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "When agreeing the remuneration, S"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and D"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "that of S"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Average rent surpluses of around DM 28,300 per year over the past 10 years"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has written off the property, the cost of which was 450,000 DM, normally"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In 1982 he re-covered the roof of the house for 50,000 DM"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In accordance with Section 82b EStDV, he has spread the costs over 5 years"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "When he submitted his income tax declaration in 1984, he applied for the income from the usufruct appointment to be distributed over 15 years"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "uses the property from November 1, 1984 as follows: 7 apartments are rented to third parties at DM 600 per month each; D uses 2 apartments"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "himself, one for his own residential purposes and one for his law firm"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "D has another apartment"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "by contract of 1 1 1984 to his adult son Claus (C"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") for the duration of the course, initially made available for use free of charge until November 1, 1990"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In 1984 D spent a total of DM 18,000 in running costs including repair costs for the house"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution The issue is a usufructuary right that has been ordered against payment (Item 7)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has to tax the income from the rented apartments (cf."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "10 f"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "For one's own apartment and the apartment left to the son as well as for the apartment used as a law firm, D"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "no value in use to be recognized (Item 27)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The cost of the property plus the depreciation on the usufructuary right (Item 28; 1/15 of 300,000 DM = 20,000 DM) can be D"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Deduct income-related expenses (Item 29) to the extent that they relate to the apartments rented out to third parties"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "For the owner-occupied apartment (Item 30) and the son's apartment (Item 54 d), D cannot deduct any income-related expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Insofar as the costs are attributable to the professional apartment, they are to be borne by D"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "deductible as business expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The value in use of the son's apartment must be taxed according to Section 21 (2) second alternative EStG (Item 54)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The payment for the usufruct is to be recorded at S in principle in full in 1984 as income from VuV (Item 31)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "It can be evenly distributed over a maximum of 10 years (Item 32)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "can continue to claim the depreciation for the building (Item 33) and claim the maintenance costs not yet used"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessment 1984 D"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income VuV rented apartments (4,200 DM x 12) 50,400 DM Advertising costs, running costs (18,000 DM), depreciation right of usufruct (20,000 DM), a total of 38,000 DM of which 7/1026,600 DMIncome from VuV 23,3,800 DMOperating expenses for income from self-employed work 1/10 of 38,000 DM3800 DMESt - Assessment 1984 C"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV (600 DM x 12) 7200 DMESt assessment 1984 p"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV Fee for usufruct 300,000 DM of which 1/1030000 DM Advertising costs Major maintenance costs 1/5 of 50,000 DM10000 DMAfA 2 v"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Of 450000 DM 9000 DM income from VuV 11000 DM3 Partly for consideration ordered usufruct 31 At the beginning of January 1979 Christian Hausmann (H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") acquired a rental property with 5 apartments for 500,000 DM (including land costs of 100,000 DM)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "By notarial contract dated 15 1 1979, H granted his parents lifelong real right to live in an apartment"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "His parents (E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") provided him with DM 40,000 in connection with the purchase of the property"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "After the death of the first deceased parent, the right of residence should belong to the survivor alone"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Father H."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "was 65 years old at the time the right of residence was ordered, the mother 55 years old"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The local rent for the parents' apartment and the other apartments is DM 600 per month"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has borne all expenses for the house with the exception of the cost of cosmetic repairs in all apartments"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The expenses of the H for the house for 1982 to 1984 amounted to 20,000 DM each year"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The parents spent 1000 DM annually on cosmetic repairs for the apartment they used"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The income tax assessments 1979 to 1981 of the H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and the E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "are final"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The payment of the E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "in the amount of 40000 DM is in the assessment of the H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "for 1979 not recorded as income from VuV"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The income tax assessments 1982 by H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "were not yet carried out at the time of the publication of the usufructuary decree of 15 November 1984"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution According to Item 8 of the usufructuary decree of 23 November 1983, a right of residence ordered completely free of charge was assumed"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "On the other hand, according to paragraph 8 of the usufructuary decree of 11/15/1984, a partially paid appointment of the right of residence is to be assumed"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The value of the right of residence at the time of the order was DM 89,330 (annual rent DM 7200 x 12,407 - duplicator according to Appendix"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "9 to the BewG if the beneficiaries are 55 years of age)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The right of residence is therefore to 448 v"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "against payment and at 552 v"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "ordered free of charge"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The income from the partial payment of the right of residence cannot be recorded at H in 1982 because no inflow was made in 1982"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "A change in the assessment for 1979 is only possible if the AO correction provisions allow this"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "can deduct the property costs incurred by the parents' apartment as income-related expenses insofar as the apartment has been made available against payment (Item 35a in conjunction with"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Item 33 and 66)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "If the right of residence was ordered free of charge, the E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "to tax the value in use of your apartment in accordance with Section 21 (2) second alternative EStG (Item 35a i"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Item 54a and 66)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Costs borne for cosmetic repairs cannot be taken into account - not even proportionally - as advertising costs, because such costs are not included in the value in use"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessments 1982 ff H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuVa) third-party rented apartments (4 x 7200 DM) 28800 DMb) parents' apartment0 DMAfA and other income-related expenses 28,000 DM of which: a) third-party rented apartments 80%"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "22400 DMb) Parents' home 20 percent"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "(DM 5600) of which deductible 448 per cent"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "2509 DM income from VuV 3891 DMESt assessments 1982 ff E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Since the E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "the usufruct to 552 BC"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has been ordered free of charge, you have to pay tax on the difference between the rent customary in the location and the rent actually paid; So it is to them 552 BC"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "to be added to the annual rent of DM 7200 = DM 3974 (Item 35a in conjunction with"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Item 54 a)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "32 Variant of the facts (transitional regulation in accordance with Item 66) H."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "applies for the assessment for 1982 that the partial remuneration for ordering the right of residence is not added to him, d"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "he would like to continue to deduct the advertising expenses in full"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has submitted a declaration from his parents that they agree to be treated for tax purposes in accordance with the previous administrative practice"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The parents have agreed to continue to tax the value in use of their apartment in full for 1982 and 1983 (Item 66 in conjunction with"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Based on the regulation in Item 66, it can still be assumed up to and including VZ 1983 that the right of residence was ordered entirely free of charge"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "accordingly does not have to pay tax on the partial payment or the value in use of his parents' apartment"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "However, in accordance with the transitional regulations mentioned under 11, he can deduct the property costs incurred on the parents' apartment in full up to and including VZ 1983 as income-related expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The regulation in Item 66 is an equity measure i"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Section 163 AO"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The prerequisite for the application of the regulation at H is that the entitled residents pay full tax on the value in use of their apartment for 1982 and 1983"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The equity measure for H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "is therefore to be met under the subsequent condition of taxation of the value in use for the beneficiaries"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The condition and the consequences of its non-fulfillment are in an annex to the tax assessment of the H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "(reference to Rdvfg"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "from 12 3 1985 S-2227 - 76 - St 11 - 31 ESt-Nr 16/19 85 to \u00a7 21 EStG)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The application of Item 66 in the 1982 ESt assessment of entitled residents requires that they also tax the value in use for 1983"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In an annex to the 1982 tax assessment, it should therefore be pointed out that the equity regulation is subject to the subsequent condition that the value in use for 1983 is also attributed to the entitled residents"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessment 1982 H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV rented apartment 28800 IN parents 'apartment DM 0 Commercial expenses from third-party rented apartments22400 DM Parents' apartment DM 5600Income from VuV800 DMESt assessment 1982 E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income from VuV value in use of the apartment 7200 DM33 Variant of circumstances (transitional regulation according to Item 66) Situation as in 32; in the 1983 income tax assessment of the H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "the income was determined as for 1982 (see 32)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "insist, however, in their 1983 income tax assessment, that the value in use is only added to them to the extent that they use the apartment free of charge"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution The prerequisites for the application of the equity regulation according to"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "66 with the income tax assessments 1982 and 1983 of the H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and in the 1982 ESt assessment of the E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "are no longer available"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The determination of the income from the apartment of E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "is to be carried out for 1983 as in example 31"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The 1982 income tax assessment for H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Any measure of equity taken is to be revoked"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The decision on the revocation of the equity measure constitutes a basic decision within the meaning of \u00a7 175 Paragraph 1 Clause 1 No. 1 AO with the result that the 1982 income tax assessments of the H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and the E"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "as well as the income tax assessment 1983 of the H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "must be corrected accordingly (determination of income as in example 31)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessments 1984 ff H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The transitional regulation in Item 66 is no longer applicable"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Taxation must be carried out as in example 31"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "34 Situation variant (transitional regulation according to Item 66) When submitting the income tax declaration for 1983, H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The application of the transitional regulation according to Item 66 exclusively for the VZ 1983 Solution The application cannot be complied with because it had to be submitted for the first assessment period for which a final assessment is not yet available; this was the assessment period 1982 Changes H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "does not submit his application despite appropriate instruction, the income from VuV is therefore to be determined as for 1982"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "35 Factual variant (replacement) In March 1985, H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and his parents the redemption of the right of residence with effect from 1 1 1984 against repayment of an amount of 32,000 DM"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "At the same time they conclude with effect"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "1 1 1984 signed a lease (rent 600 DM per month), so that H"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "transfers only an amount of 23,000 DM to his parents in March 1985 (32,000 DM less rent for 15 months)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The amount of DM 32,000 is to be used to reimburse the portion of the salary of DM 40,000 that was not yet used up to 1 November 1984"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Retroactive redemption is permitted (Item 61)"},