he 1983 ESt notification of the couple P"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ", in which the value in use of the apartment used by you has been recorded, is already final"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The application of the transitional regulation in Item 63 is not applicable to the married couple S."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "because of the validity of the income tax assessment of the couple P"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "not permitted"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The determination of the income is to be carried out as with 61"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "64 Situation variant Situation as for 61; however, the property was transferred on December 31, 1982"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution The value in use of the apartment of the spouses S."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "is to be determined according to \u00a7 21a EStG"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The unit value of the property is to be divided between the two apartments for the purpose of determining the income (Section 164b Paragraph 14 Sentence 2 ESt\u00c4R 1984)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The proportional share of the apartment of the couple P"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Due to the lack of income for the spouses S"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "not to be considered as advertising expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The deduction of a permanent burden is also out of the question (see judgment of the BFH of 7 12 1982 BStBl 1983 II p"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "660)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The couple P"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "have to tax the value in use of their apartment in accordance with Section 21 Paragraph 2 Second Alternative EStG (Section 162 Paragraph 1 ESt\u00c4R 1984 and No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Section 21a of the Income Tax Act is not applicable in this respect"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "65 Situation variant Situation as for 64; the spouses S"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "and P"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "apply, however, before carrying out the final income tax assessments in 1983, jointly the application of the transitional regulation according to No."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "63- Solution The value in use for the whole house is to be determined according to \u00a7 21a EStG and the spouses S."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "attributable"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "If necessary, you can"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "for 1983 still higher deductions according to \u00a7 7b EStG or \u00a7 82a EStDV in full as income-related expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "From 1984 the income from VuV is to be determined as in 64"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "7 Reserved usufruct in the case of transfer of property against payment 71 Reserved usufruct in rem, Ms. Steinmann (St"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") sold their debt-free house for DM 300,000 to Mr.Lamp (L."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": ") sold"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The value of the land is DM 80,000"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has at the same time reserved the lifelong real usufructuary right"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "She had reached the age of 75 when the contract was signed"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The value of the usufruct amounts to 7,000 DM annually"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "continued to live in the house himself and paid the land costs"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "in 1984 had a new heating system installed in the house for 15,000 DM"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution St."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "As the usufructuary of the single-family house, the value in use continues to be taxed in accordance with Section 21a EStG (Item 39)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "no income from VuV is to be attributed for 1984; He cannot therefore deduct any advertising expenses (Item 44)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "72 Situation variant (obligatory \"reservation\" usufruct) Situation as for 71; however, the usufruct is not entered in the land register"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Solution It is an obligatory usufructuary right that is ordered against payment"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "In contrast to Example 71, there is no reserved usufruct for income tax purposes"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Because of the lack of entry in the land register, it can be assumed that L"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Has become the owner of an unencumbered property and he as the new owner of St"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has granted the usufructuary right"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The transfer of real estate and the usufruct are to be treated for tax purposes as if St"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "the property for 343,071 DM (300,000 DM plus the value of the usufruct according to Annex 9 to the BewG: 7,000 DM x 6153 = 43071 DM) would have been sold for cash payments of 300,000 DM and offset against the claim of L."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "at St."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "from the justification of the right of use (Item 53 b)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "uses the house like a tenant"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Therefore, no value in use can be assigned to it"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "It cannot deduct the property costs as income-related expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "has income from VuV in 1984 equal to the value of the usufruct. He can apply for this to be evenly distributed over a maximum of 10 years (Item 53b i"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Item 32)"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "can deduct the costs borne by him for the heating renewal and the depreciation for the building as business expenses"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "The purchase price of the property also includes the value of the usufruct"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "Income tax assessment St."}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "1984 Income from VuV0 DMESt assessment L"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "1984 Income from VuV Fee for the usufruct43071 DM of which on application 1/104307 DM Advertising costs Renewal of heating 15000 DMAfA 2 v"}, {"meta": {"name": "0061693.xml"}, "text": "of (343 071 DM minus 80000 DM) 263 071 DM 52 62 DM loss from VuV15955 DM --- income tax / wage tax / church tax North Rhine-Westphalia"}]